All Classes

Class Description
CSVExporter
CSVExporter class is for export DataTable object into CSV format.
CSVRow
CSVRow class is for mapping loaded data from CSV file.
DataLoader
The DataLoader class is used to read data from the given file.
DataTable
The DataTable class is used for working with loaded data.
DataTableRow
DataTableRow class is for selected data by user.
DataTableTest
Test class for DataTable class methods.
Exporter
Interface for exporting data.
HTMLExporter
HTMLExporter class is for export DataTable object into HTML format.
Main
Main class.
XLSXExporter
XLSXExporter class is for export DataTable object into XLSX format.
